# Alchemy detective

## Section I - Game Overview

We are alchemist and we are tasked with finding information about shadow sociaty that wants to overthrown current ruler. Player will have to use their skills and wits to solve this puzzle 

### Genre

point and click adventure / paper please type of a game 


### Game Flow Summary

player is sent to various rooms in which they can find items around it, using alchemical knowledge they can find clues which will solve the game

introduction of a room
items in a room like:
> papers
> weapons
> dokuments 
> money etc

using alchemical items like:
 iodine, cyanoacrylate, silver nitrate and ninhydrin
to find finger prints, sweat stains, blood stains, hidden texts etc. 

each room have limitted time after which player has to choose perpetrator or other solution to a puzzle

### Scope

main menu 
pick a room 
room 
items in a room 

### gameflow 

point and click adventure with papers please.

